author: AsapSCIENCE
description:
Erectile dysfunction is on the rise for young men, leading to what researchers are calling a "crisis in male sexuality". The scientific reasons why men are struggling to "get hard" are surprising and fascinating - today we break down all the science and ways it could be fixed.
